SpoonerPlacements.Note: Sure, you can turbo your hyperbike through jumps, rings, and tubes and make it look easy - but can you deal with the Vespucci canals? Rusting strollers, ex-FIB informants, the flaming wreckage of hovercars and amphibious quads - sometimes the naturally occurring obstacles are the trickiest. Lap Transform Race starting on motorcycles, also featuring the Deluxo, Blazer Aqua and Thruster.
